Game is fast, fun, and creative. My only gripe is some glitches that 
occurred during gameplay, specifically around the end of level 2. I would 
turn invisible while doing certain actions! I also don't like the screen 
ratio, I understand you need space for the buttons at the bottom, but I 
think it would be better if the game was full screen (18:9 in my case) and 
when I need to go home, be able to swipe up into the screen that it 
currently is. Fix these issues as well as add more content and you've got 
yourself a super fancy game to play!
